{
  "stem": "25287.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Soon as somebody-- then they took the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when we go out front of the barrack, it was so cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we stand next to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we talked about food and singing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And took me 52 years, when I find it out this tune name, what we were singing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We make this song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You will read [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Marta ?] books, you know, because if I tell you Hungarian, you don't understand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want I-- I--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's silly, really, but a week ago Thursday-- I told you I teaching, still volunteer-- so five or six, you know, senior, asking about the Holocaust and things, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, oh, I just want to tell you nice things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We even make some parody sung-- song in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I cannot tell you what the tune.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one of the women is a very good musician, you know, and a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I sing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, Ilona, this is 'Lili Marleen' song.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it took me 52, and, you know, I just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know the real Hungarian version.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But what-- what we make it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SINGING] The song is about we are outside, and we talking about food, and the freezing, and when the German came and counting us, and always miss two, three children, and how they said then we have to kneel, and every 10 get killed.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then the gong, you know, hear is so good, because we just dream, because we're going in and going to have nice warm food and warm blanket.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we think about how going to grow our hair-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The hardest thing was, in Auschwitz, when they selecting us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
